# Integration Testing Suite for A1-Inter-LLM-Com

## Overview
This document outlines the comprehensive integration testing strategy for the A1-Inter-LLM-Com multi-agent communication platform.

## Test Environment Setup

### Prerequisites
- Node.js 18+
- PostgreSQL 13+ (or SQLite for development)
- Redis 6+ (optional, for advanced features)
- Chrome/Chromium (for extension testing)
- Docker (for containerized testing)

### Environment Configuration
```bash
# Test environment variables
export NODE_ENV=test
export TEST_DATABASE_URL=postgresql://test:test@localhost:5432/agency_hub_test
export TEST_REDIS_URL=redis://localhost:6379/1
export TEST_PORT=3010
export TEST_WS_PORT=3012
export LOG_LEVEL=warn
```

### Setup Commands
```bash
# Install test dependencies
npm install --dev

# Setup test database
npm run db:create:test
npm run migrate:test

# Start test services
npm run test:setup

# Run integration tests
npm run test:integration
```

