### 2. Message Routing Integration Tests

#### Point-to-Point Communication
```javascript
describe('Message Routing', () => {
  test('should route message between registered agents', async () => {
    // Setup agents
    const sender = await registerAgent('sender-agent');
    const recipient = await registerAgent('recipient-agent');
    
    const message = {
      type: 'TASK_REQUEST',
